\toprule
& brain-fwi & Sonus & Stride \\
\midrule
Solver & j-Wave (PSTD, JAX) & Stride/Devito (FD) & Devito (FD) \\
Gradients & JAX autodiff & Adjoint-state & Adjoint-state \\
GPU backend & JAX/XLA native & Devito OpenACC & Devito OpenACC \\
